pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: BLOG
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - styles.css

pagetitle: BLOG
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  theme: cosmo
  listing:
    contents: posts
    sort: date desc
    type: grid
    feed: false
    categories: true
    sort-ui: true
    filter-ui: true
    fields:
      - image
      - date
      - title
      - description
  page-layout: full
  title-block-banner: true
